<div class="language-r highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">lorenz</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">df</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">%&gt;%</span><span class="w">
