<p><img src="/images/fga-dist-unnamed-chunk-12-1.png" title="plot of chunk unnamed-chunk-12" alt="plot of chunk unnamed-chunk-12" width="100%" /></p>

<p>For an example of their abnormal shot distribution, we need not look further than the box score from their last game of the season, a game in which Russell Westbrook hoisted 43 shots.</p>

